<heading id="5D2F81A28E3B674247C0E6AEFDBB6DCF" bold="true" box="[151,605,222,248]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" reason="1">
<emphasis id="34ACEADC8E3B674247C0E6AEFDBB6DCF" bold="true" box="[151,605,222,248]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Family 
<taxonomicName id="C1D84D4D8E3B674247A1E6AEFDBB6DCF" authority="Bellardi, 1875" authorityName="Bellardi" authorityYear="1875" box="[246,605,222,248]" class="Gastropoda" family="Raphitomidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">
Raphitomidae 
<bibRefCitation id="62494B3F8E3B674246F8E6AEFDBB6DCF" author="Bellardi" box="[431,605,222,248]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Bellardi, L. (1875) Novae pleurotomidarum Pedimonti et Liguriae fossilium: dispositionis prodromus. Bullettino della Societa Malacologica Italiana, 1, 16 - 24." type="journal article" year="1875">
Bellardi, 
<number id="B01024E98E3B67424575E6AEFDBB6DCF" box="[546,605,222,248]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1875.0">1875</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="066736CE8E3B674247C0E755FE746E02" blockId="4.[151,1436,293,822]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
The taxon 
<taxonomicName id="C1D84D4D8E3B67424641E755FE5E6C0A" box="[278,440,293,317]" class="Gastropoda" family="Raphitomidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Raphitomidae</taxonomicName>
was established by 
<bibRefCitation id="62494B3F8E3B674245F1E755FC616C0A" author="Bellardi" box="[678,903,293,317]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Bellardi, L. (1875) Novae pleurotomidarum Pedimonti et Liguriae fossilium: dispositionis prodromus. Bullettino della Societa Malacologica Italiana, 1, 16 - 24." type="journal article" year="1875">
Bellardi (
<number id="B01024E98E3B67424442E755FCB26C0A" box="[789,852,293,317]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1875.0">1875</number>
: 
<number id="B01024E98E3B67424436E755FC996C0A" box="[865,895,293,317]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="22.0">22</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
to include small species with turreted shells, anal sinus close to the suture, smooth columella and without an operculum. The 
<typeStatus id="D963886C8E3B674243DBE73AFB586C55" box="[1164,1214,330,354]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">type</typeStatus>
genus 
<taxonomicName id="C1D84D4D8E3B6742424AE739FEA36CB2" authority="Bellardi, 1847" authorityName="Bellardi" authorityYear="1847" class="Gastropoda" family="Raphitomidae" genus="Raphitoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="34ACEADC8E3B6742424AE739FA7A6C56" box="[1309,1436,329,353]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Raphitoma</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="62494B3F8E3B674247C0E71DFEA36CB2" author="Bellardi" box="[151,325,365,389]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Bellardi, L. (1847) Monografia delle Pleurotome fossili del Piemonte. Memorie della Reale Accademia delle Scienze di Torino, serie 2, 9, 531 - 650, 4 pls." type="journal article" year="1847">
Bellardi, 
<number id="B01024E98E3B6742465CE71DFEA36CB2" box="[267,325,365,389]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1847.0">1847</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is somewhat problematic, as a 
<typeStatus id="D963886C8E3B67424588E71EFCF76CB1" box="[735,785,366,390]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">type</typeStatus>
species was not designated and subsequent authors suggested different 
<typeStatus id="D963886C8E3B674246D3E7E2FE506C9D" box="[388,438,402,426]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">type</typeStatus>
species, creating much confusion over this issue. In the same paper in which the 
<taxonomicName id="C1D84D4D8E3B674247C0E7C5FEDF6CFA" box="[151,313,437,461]" class="Gastropoda" family="Raphitomidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Raphitomidae</taxonomicName>
was proposed, 
<bibRefCitation id="62494B3F8E3B674246B9E7C5FD796CFA" author="Bellardi" box="[494,671,437,461]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Bellardi, L. (1875) Novae pleurotomidarum Pedimonti et Liguriae fossilium: dispositionis prodromus. Bullettino della Societa Malacologica Italiana, 1, 16 - 24." type="journal article" year="1875">
Bellardi (
<number id="B01024E98E3B6742450CE7C5FD716CFA" box="[603,663,437,461]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1875.0">1875</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
mentioned 
<taxonomicName id="C1D84D4D8E3B6742447EE7C5FB5B6CFA" authority="Brocci, 1814" authorityName="Brocci" authorityYear="1814" box="[809,1213,437,461]" class="Gastropoda" family="Raphitomidae" genus="Raphitoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="vulpecula">
<emphasis id="34ACEADC8E3B6742447EE7C5FBF96CFA" box="[809,1055,437,461]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Raphitoma vulpecula</emphasis>
Brocci, 
<number id="B01024E98E3B674243D4E7C5FB5B6CFA" box="[1155,1213,437,461]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1814.0">1814</number>
</taxonomicName>
as the 
<typeStatus id="D963886C8E3B67424258E7C6FAA76CF9" box="[1295,1345,438,462]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">type</typeStatus>
species of this genus. However, the earliest designation of a 
<typeStatus id="D963886C8E3B67424452E7AAFCD16CC5" box="[773,823,474,498]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">type</typeStatus>
species was by 
<bibRefCitation id="62494B3F8E3B674244AFE7AAFB046CC6" author="Monterosato" box="[1016,1250,473,497]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Monterosato, M. (1875) Nuova rivista delle conchiglie mediterranee. Atti dell'Accademia di Scienze, Lettere ed Arti di Palermo, nuova serie, 5, 1 - 50." type="journal article" year="1875">
Monterosato (
<number id="B01024E98E3B674243CCE7A9FB3F6CC6" box="[1179,1241,473,497]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1875.0">1875</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, who appointed 
<taxonomicName id="C1D84D4D8E3B674247C0E78DFD436F22" authority="De Cristofori &amp; Jan, 1832" authorityName="De Cristofori &amp; Jan" authorityYear="1832" box="[151,677,509,533]" class="Gastropoda" family="Raphitomidae" genus="Raphitoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="hystrix">
<emphasis id="34ACEADC8E3B674247C0E78DFE8A6F22" box="[151,364,509,533]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Raphitoma hystrix</emphasis>
De 
<bibRefCitation id="62494B3F8E3B674246CBE78DFD436F22" author="Cristofori" box="[412,677,509,533]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Cristofori, J. de &amp; Jan, G. (1832) Catalogus in IV Sectiones Divisus rerum Naturalium in Museo Exstantium Josephi de Christofori et Georgio Jan Plurinum Acad. Scient. et Societ. Nat. Cur. Sodalium ecc. Sectio II. Pars I. Conchylia Fossilia ex Formatione Telluris Tertiaria in Collectione Nostra Exstantia. Carmignani, Parma, 16 pp., 1 pl." type="book" year="1832">
Cristofori &amp; Jan, 
<number id="B01024E98E3B6742453FE78DFD436F22" box="[616,677,509,533]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1832.0">1832</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. This species was also the first to be mentioned under 
<taxonomicName id="C1D84D4D8E3B6742424AE78DFA7A6F22" box="[1309,1436,509,533]" class="Gastropoda" family="Raphitomidae" genus="Raphitoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="34ACEADC8E3B6742424AE78DFA7A6F22" box="[1309,1436,509,533]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Raphitoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the original description of the genus (
<bibRefCitation id="62494B3F8E3B674245D5E451FC976F0E" author="Bellardi" box="[642,881,545,569]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Bellardi, L. (1847) Monografia delle Pleurotome fossili del Piemonte. Memorie della Reale Accademia delle Scienze di Torino, serie 2, 9, 531 - 650, 4 pls." type="journal article" year="1847">
Bellardi, 
<number id="B01024E98E3B674245A3E451FCD46F0E" box="[756,818,545,569]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1847.0">1847</number>
: 
<number id="B01024E98E3B67424416E451FC976F0E" box="[833,881,545,569]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="613.0">613</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). Van Aarsten 
<emphasis id="34ACEADC8E3B67424370E452FBB86F0E" box="[1063,1118,545,569]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">et al</emphasis>
. (
<number id="B01024E98E3B6742432EE451FB5E6F0E" box="[1145,1208,545,569]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1984.0">1984</number>
: 
<number id="B01024E98E3B67424390E451FB036F0E" box="[1223,1253,545,569]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="89.0">89</number>
) noted another complication, as 
<taxonomicName id="C1D84D4D8E3B67424608E435FDD96F6A" box="[351,575,581,605]" class="Gastropoda" family="Turridae" genus="Pleurotoma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="hystrix">
<emphasis id="34ACEADC8E3B67424608E435FDD96F6A" box="[351,575,581,605]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Pleurotoma hystrix</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was published without a description or illustration (De 
<bibRefCitation id="62494B3F8E3B67424382E435FF336FB6" author="Cristofori" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Cristofori, J. de &amp; Jan, G. (1832) Catalogus in IV Sectiones Divisus rerum Naturalium in Museo Exstantium Josephi de Christofori et Georgio Jan Plurinum Acad. Scient. et Societ. Nat. Cur. Sodalium ecc. Sectio II. Pars I. Conchylia Fossilia ex Formatione Telluris Tertiaria in Collectione Nostra Exstantia. Carmignani, Parma, 16 pp., 1 pl." type="book" year="1832">
Cristofori &amp; Jan, 
<number id="B01024E98E3B674247C0E419FF336FB6" box="[151,213,617,641]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1832.0">1832</number>
</bibRefCitation>
: 
<number id="B01024E98E3B674247B5E419FEE66FB6" box="[226,256,617,641]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="10.0">10</number>
) and is therefore a 
<emphasis id="34ACEADC8E3B674246BBE41AFD766FB6" box="[492,656,617,641]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">nomen nudum</emphasis>
. Van Aarsten 
<emphasis id="34ACEADC8E3B6742446CE41AFC976FB6" box="[827,881,617,641]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">et al</emphasis>
. (
<number id="B01024E98E3B674244DDE419FC206FB6" box="[906,966,617,641]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1984.0">1984</number>
) considered the species as validated by 
<bibRefCitation id="62494B3F8E3B674247C0E4FDFEAA6F92" author="Bellardi" box="[151,332,653,677]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Bellardi, L. (1847) Monografia delle Pleurotome fossili del Piemonte. Memorie della Reale Accademia delle Scienze di Torino, serie 2, 9, 531 - 650, 4 pls." type="journal article" year="1847">
Bellardi (
<number id="B01024E98E3B67424652E4FDFEA26F92" box="[261,324,653,677]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1847.0">1847</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, even though Bellardi used a different spelling of the name 
<taxonomicName id="C1D84D4D8E3B6742435FE4FDFB3F6F92" box="[1032,1241,653,677]" class="Gastropoda" family="Raphitomidae" genus="Raphitoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="histrix">
<emphasis id="34ACEADC8E3B6742435FE4FDFB3F6F92" box="[1032,1241,653,677]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Raphitoma histrix</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and illustrated a specimen that is quite different from De Cristofori &amp; Jan’s 
<typeStatus id="D963886C8E3B67424417E4C2FC946FFD" box="[832,882,690,714]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">type</typeStatus>
material (illustrated in 
<bibRefCitation id="62494B3F8E3B674243D7E4C1FAE86FFE" author="Pinna" box="[1152,1294,689,713]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Pinna, G. (1971) I tipi delle specie di Gasteropodi terziari istituite da Guiseppe De Cristofori e Giorgo Jan nel 1832 conservate nelle collezioni del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Milano. Atti della Societa Italiana de Scienze Naturale e del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale de Milano, 112, 421 - 440, pls. 76 - 77." type="journal article" year="1971">
Pinna, 
<number id="B01024E98E3B67424387E4C1FAE86FFE" box="[1232,1294,689,713]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1971.0">1971</number>
</bibRefCitation>
: 
<number id="B01024E98E3B6742424EE4C1FAA16FFE" box="[1305,1351,689,713]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="440.0">440</number>
, pl. 
<number id="B01024E98E3B67424220E4C1FA716FFE" box="[1399,1431,689,713]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="76.0">76</number>
, fig. 
<number id="B01024E98E3B6742479CE4A5FF3F6FDA" box="[203,217,725,749]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1.0">1</number>
). It seems that 
<taxonomicName id="C1D84D4D8E3B674246F6E4A5FCC86FDA" authority="Bellardi, 1847" authorityName="Bellardi" authorityYear="1847" box="[417,814,725,749]" class="Gastropoda" family="Raphitomidae" genus="Raphitoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="histrix">
<emphasis id="34ACEADC8E3B674246F6E4A5FD916FDA" box="[417,631,725,749]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Raphitoma histrix</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="62494B3F8E3B674245D3E4A5FCC86FDA" author="Bellardi" box="[644,814,725,749]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Bellardi, L. (1847) Monografia delle Pleurotome fossili del Piemonte. Memorie della Reale Accademia delle Scienze di Torino, serie 2, 9, 531 - 650, 4 pls." type="journal article" year="1847">
Bellardi, 
<number id="B01024E98E3B674245A2E4A5FCC86FDA" box="[757,814,725,749]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1847.0">1847</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is not the same species as 
<taxonomicName id="C1D84D4D8E3B674243DCE4A5FE7C6E26" authority="De Cristofori &amp; Jan, 1832" authorityName="De Cristofori &amp; Jan" authorityYear="1832" class="Gastropoda" family="Turridae" genus="Pleurotoma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="hystrix">
<emphasis id="34ACEADC8E3B674243DCE4A5FA886FDA" box="[1163,1390,725,749]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Pleurotoma hystrix</emphasis>
De 
<bibRefCitation id="62494B3F8E3B674247C0E489FE7C6E26" author="Cristofori" box="[151,410,761,785]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refString="Cristofori, J. de &amp; Jan, G. (1832) Catalogus in IV Sectiones Divisus rerum Naturalium in Museo Exstantium Josephi de Christofori et Georgio Jan Plurinum Acad. Scient. et Societ. Nat. Cur. Sodalium ecc. Sectio II. Pars I. Conchylia Fossilia ex Formatione Telluris Tertiaria in Collectione Nostra Exstantia. Carmignani, Parma, 16 pp., 1 pl." type="book" year="1832">
Cristofori &amp; Jan, 
<number id="B01024E98E3B67424637E489FE7C6E26" box="[352,410,761,785]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1832.0">1832</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and that the latter species, validated by Pinna’s publication, is the correct 
<typeStatus id="D963886C8E3B674243A7E48AFAC46E25" box="[1264,1314,762,786]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">type</typeStatus>
